synopsis: Lingering doubt? Check. Butt-clenching fear? Check. Bottom moist? Check-arooni! Mark's crippling sense of doubt over his impending nuptials is steamrollered by Sophie's relentless quest to get married and have a baby. Perhaps Jeremy sleeping with her mother will help? But then again, perhaps not...
